{"tid":1715843,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑警正在散播恐懼","createTime":"2019-11-13T07:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T11:34:23.000Z","uid":222614,"like":787,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":116,"replies":[{"pid":"1be5534e31f5070d6a1641765e0e163960b83155","tid":1715843,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:43:18.000Z","msg":"經過二號橋之戰，香港人及中大生成功守住中大，士氣大增。黑警見強攻無果，今日就轉打心理戰。<br />\n<br />\n接近中午時份，黑警開始在各大網上平台放風，聲稱「已將中大包圍」，「死守既會變成烈士」等等，用恐嚇口吻試圖削弱矢志堅守校園之一眾學生既鬥志，以及恐嚇幫助中大生香港人，意圖利用佢地既軟弱將大學生勸退。<br />\n<br />\n更可笑者，有疑似為黑警效力既網民聲稱「比警甴入到間無人無物資嘅學校係無損失」，意思即係同學生講「你地帶埋啲物資走啦，畀我地入中大啦」。如此下流之術，只有愚昧既人先會中計。"},{"pid":"43093539d5bd5c3aaab1a5c8e978e22915dbeec4","tid":1715843,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:43:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"261001511accb493d9425540e02b26fc31c4f7b8","tid":1715843,"uid":78132,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:43:52.000Z","msg":"無ddos 大家明啦"},{"pid":"6cf95326bcf9dc3e8c51d250656d91400f9f44bf","tid":1715843,"uid":196666,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:44:27.000Z","msg":"同意 中大人最清楚自己狀況"},{"pid":"ba7c9cad9fee7fa6ec3d39b477ae8d3730edf08e","tid":1715843,"uid":276440,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:44:49.000Z","msg":"毅進仔智商係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634a707abb1afbcce57d0f0dde9b4b7f9ad0eae8","tid":1715843,"uid":295459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:45:00.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講得好岩"},{"pid":"5cd14f02bbf77263708e1cac27b6a1b2112f404f","tid":1715843,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4279bcb1c64fd97a291e6de467b52a9410d301","tid":1715843,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited